vote-punish.name: Vote-Punish
vote-punish.description:
Your Staff isn't always verfügbar, and that's alright. With this you can prepare for that Situation and let your Chat moderate itself.

**How it works**
> 1. A Mitglied mentions @Staff to notify them
> 2. Ayako waits for a Staff Mitglied to write something in chat until the Cooldown wears off
> -# A Staff-Mitglied sending a Nachricht, reacting to Ayako's Reaktion or executing a Punishment counts as appearing
> 3. If no Staff Mitglied appears in time, Ayako will lock the Kanal and ask the Benutzer who mentioned which Mitglied this Mention is about.
> 4. Ayako will then start a Vote to decide if the mentioned Mitglied should be punished.
> -# - Only Mitglieder with the required Rolle can vote. 
> -# - If no required Rolle is set everyone can vote.
> -# - The vote requires at least the Amount of Votes you specified to pass.
> 5. If the Vote passes, Ayako will execute the Punishment you specified for the specified Duration.
> 6. Ayako will unlock the Kanal again.

ping-reporter.name: Ping-Report
ping-reporter.description:
Discord's Push-Notification delivery is somewhat unreliable on large servers.
**Note:** This requires the Rolle to have less than 100 Mitglieder

**How it works**
> 1. A Mitglied mentions @Staff to notify them
> -# - On large Servers Discord will go through every Mitglied and check if they are elligible for a Notification at a very slow Rate. Causing up to Hour long Delays on Push-Notifications
> 2. Ayako sends a Log-Nachricht into your specified Kanal along with a @Mention for every of the Rollen Mitglieder
> -# - This causes Discord to start a second Notification-Process, but only on the mentioned Mitglieder. Making them receive the Push-Notification almost instantly

linked-roles-deco.desc:
## Step-by-Step Setup Guide:
> **Note** You have to erstellen a new Bot for every Linked Rolle you want to hinzufügen.
1. Select your Bot using the `Bot` Schaltfläche below
2. Insert your Bot Token using the `Bot Token` Schaltfläche below.
> You can obtain it in [Discord's Developer Portal](https://discordapp.com/developers/applications/)
> In your App's Settings Page under `Bot` using the `zurücksetzen Token` Schaltfläche
3. Insert your Bot Secret using the `Bot Secret` Schaltfläche below.
> You can obtain it in [Discord's Developer Portal](https://discordapp.com/developers/applications/)
> In your App's Settings Page under `OAuth2` using the `zurücksetzen Secret` Schaltfläche
4. Insert ```https://api.ayakobot.com/v1/guilds/{{guildId}}/linked-Rollen/{{settingsId}}/decoration``` as a Redirect URL under the `OAuth2` Section using the `hinzufügen Redirect` Schaltfläche
5. Insert the same URL into the `Linked Rollen Verification URL` under the `General Information` Section
6. Enter a Beschreibung, also under `General Information`. Text entered hier will be displayed on Benutzer-Profiles after linking the Rolle (max. 100 Characters)
7. Select the Rolle using the `Rolle` Schaltfläche
8. Go into your Server's Rolle Settings, click on the Rolle, click `Links` and Select your Bot as Requirement
9. Lastly, click `Make Visible` to make the Rolle visible next to your Username

## How to get the Rolle
### The long Way
1. Click on your Server Name
2. Click `Linked Rollen`
3. Click the Rolle you want to have
4. Finish Verification
5. Click `Finish`

### The short Way
1: Click <id:linked-Rollen:{{roleId}}>
